{
  "stem": "2533.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[DRINKS] And he said, that's what he needs, for collars and cuffs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my dear, that was from hell to heaven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I would not have last long in the laundry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But going to a sewing room, the German side of the camp, was nice and-- and clean.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And doing sewing was a lot easier then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from time to time, a German, when he was going on leave, he used to come in and ask could we make him, like for, dress up a doll or something for his wife, to take home, and all that.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was done beside what we had to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew the other girls who  were in the sewing room, but we didn't work together before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they are-- you know, the Germans sometimes, when he had a little bit of heart on the right side, used to bring in maybe a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One once brought in a piece of cake and a few cubes of sugar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The cake, we looked at it, but didn't know to eat it or look at it and something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the sugar, I-- I put away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't eat the sugar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But later when we escaped, I had the sugar with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was one that was the [INAUDIBLE] lady.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just have to-- to think about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think four or five.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that lady who was the [INAUDIBLE] lady, she was a very able person.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to embroider monograms for hankies, and monograms on under-- other things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't all the time at the machine sewing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was really, really different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not rushed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
